Definition: the quality of giving pleasure
Example: he was charmed by the sweetness of her manner; the pleasantness of a cool breeze on a hot summer day
Synonyms: adj, all, pleasant, unpleasantness, sweetness, pleasing, sweet, melodious, lovable, quality, the, of, giving, pleasure, he, was, charmed, by, her, manner, a, cool, breeze, on, hot, summer, day
Category: noun.attribute
